  "name": "AURORA-WATCH: Real-Time Drilling Surveillance Agent",
  "description": "AURORA-WATCH is the frontline sensing and monitoring agent for the AURORA drilling intelligence system. It ingests continuous real-time WITSML 2.1 data streams through the OSDU Wellbore DDMS, performs live anomaly detection on key drilling parameters, and maintains a real-time Well Health Score for every active wellbore. It is the primary alerting agent and the data provider for the AURORA-PREDICT and AURORA-ADVISE agents.",
